HEADWORD: Fuddle
<hw>Fud"dle</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To drink to excess.</def>
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fuddler</ent>⟦br⟧
